Early this week, I joined my colleagues in urging 
@POTUS to extend TPS to Ukrainians in the U.S., and I’m glad that he's acted on it.

The U.S. should be a safe haven for those escaping persecution and danger, including the brave Ukrainians who cannot return to their homeland.

@RepGusBilirakis @StateDept @DeptofDefense Fulfilling this request will only embolden Erdoğan to continue threatening instability in several strategic regions, committing human rights abuses at home and abroad, and ignoring his NATO obligations. 

This cannot happen. 
